{
  "meta": {
    "voice": null,
    "language": null,
    "rate": "1",
    "pitch": "0",
    "generatedAt": "2026-03-26T02:26:03.066Z"
  },
  "items": [
    {
      "kind": "title",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "我是谁，你是谁——学习介绍人",
      "file": "zh-cn-8c32fbd830d71d8bf5b843d47b4197a5d042beb1.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "介绍",
      "file": "zh-cn-b2f1469ad17de782fee6350f41c7a626f7a92005.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "在这节课里，我们学习说自己是谁，也学习说别人",
      "file": "zh-cn-1b33205ef8812163d81319bb10ab54e8c72894bf.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "我们用简单的句子说名字和感受",
      "file": "zh-cn-0dea4d38b1a1ec12e2c7f1ec4dbde78e60674ac5.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "我们也要记住一件重要的事：上帝认识每个人的名字",
      "file": "zh-cn-350273f552608e0a0c28fec1e01d11c8695d0ce9.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "1. 说自己",
      "file": "zh-cn-2f5d3be11d4d0ae0701542b10eebc2c4f02ff417.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "当我们说自己时，用一个特别的形式",
      "file": "zh-cn-c5cc6533323b9cda4b1fb18a6fd44f4439339bb8.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "这个形式可以说名字或感受",
      "file": "zh-cn-b6ac5de20838bc6d6c334d71fe15bd298de6a048.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "看例子：",
      "file": "zh-cn-2b52237702b27303d3a38852a8d008c52dbb825a.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "I am a boy.",
      "file": "en-us-2ea7a194959761fc6819b0a71918a66db527430d.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "I am happy.",
      "file": "en-us-23939b7341e0b2db15f437958c508b0842216b70.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "I am Moses.",
      "file": "en-us-5fd7218dba7b66e228565abe8c016114d4e7ab2c.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "这里是在说自己",
      "file": "zh-cn-efcdbccc165d044aa9642b829088fddab61535fe.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "就像说：我",
      "file": "zh-cn-c07140d4152838148e8b9078e473da11764fa021.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "2. 对别人说",
      "file": "zh-cn-a0de8dedef55e1e9709afffa0045625cac8bd84c.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "当我们直接对别人说话时，用另一种形式",
      "file": "zh-cn-5d9d8a94887c41ea6080822c0908b69d406cec93.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "看着对方说话时用",
      "file": "zh-cn-22e1317b4d0f235c27f3ada19c8f76291dc99c2c.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "看例子：",
      "file": "zh-cn-2b52237702b27303d3a38852a8d008c52dbb825a.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "You are a boy.",
      "file": "en-us-d77d87e8e23a7d0f9fa4de519606bdb500208fe4.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "You are a girl.",
      "file": "en-us-4057e5dd51af2766d75664e2de122f5da27990c9.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "You are happy.",
      "file": "en-us-d88c326c1e116ceabac6175587976a0f555d96a0.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "You are special.",
      "file": "en-us-bd168e4be2ccb03a768f5e99a6affc68421f8f80.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "这里是在对别人说",
      "file": "zh-cn-ded7f7d70aed833c601796bacd95d5e10afbaba5.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "就像说：你",
      "file": "zh-cn-e0debace47a6cf546711e01c085d1c7c114e822e.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "3. 说一个男孩或男人",
      "file": "zh-cn-f9f9bedb8ee65438d8fa6fae9ef4d209de49b84b.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "想一想，我们在说一个不在对话中的男孩",
      "file": "zh-cn-88c82a9d66e1030332ca703dc04815df2b546c8e.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "他没有说话，我们也没有直接对他说",
      "file": "zh-cn-b85aea129c7fb059df105a2d372758f1d829716e.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "我们是在和别人说他的事",
      "file": "zh-cn-ea0cb7927dde521ec650e1af32ea4d137d5908bd.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "看例子：",
      "file": "zh-cn-2b52237702b27303d3a38852a8d008c52dbb825a.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "He is a boy.",
      "file": "en-us-2a2632a545de1823da43afd6efaf7a9bdde88adf.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "He is happy.",
      "file": "en-us-82d5659b428ca8187f1b62cd7b1c594773f693e2.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "He is Moses.",
      "file": "en-us-1875dbfb2e551e944cb3613e86530d6cc03308b8.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "这里是在说一个男孩或男人",
      "file": "zh-cn-fe80848d2405b42d7575f71baa0c4d218b17a745.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "就像指着他告诉别人",
      "file": "zh-cn-e83353abc8941bb81a5431b079e222a0630d0170.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "4. 说一个女孩或女人",
      "file": "zh-cn-d7bfc8262c10bfdc70aca2d7511636793d48d4a1.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "我们也可以说一个女孩或女人",
      "file": "zh-cn-acb6bc6083630423eb5975d7acb8c081128e8110.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "她没有说话，我们也没有直接对她说",
      "file": "zh-cn-1e197fea6a2f489758517b3f52a4c4afa16bb95f.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "我们是在说她",
      "file": "zh-cn-ac4dcc23fc4f450eed25021860b56117092cd35c.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "看例子：",
      "file": "zh-cn-2b52237702b27303d3a38852a8d008c52dbb825a.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "She is a girl.",
      "file": "en-us-30ddae33c2bccaca73a4be47e7712fd4c9bfcf94.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "She is happy.",
      "file": "en-us-d1b3d3c880ee376906cd771d820b9756e0aed280.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "She is Hannah.",
      "file": "en-us-d1fcfedd52306f6c11995ac3e30ad2bbc7bf56f6.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "这里是在说一个女孩或女人",
      "file": "zh-cn-e82bcd8a856655e0594bfd7c0efa1535640ca94d.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "就像指着她告诉别人",
      "file": "zh-cn-6c8bfd0bf90235a1e2817b658a369bdb0b3049df.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "5. 上帝认识你",
      "file": "zh-cn-429aac74ef4156b8f52ca13fdea28c92ca82df84.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "上帝认识每个人的名字",
      "file": "zh-cn-111b3c16f1d04d334e6e740999200291ef5240a8.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "你很重要，也很特别",
      "file": "zh-cn-28076a7e5300e14e3930cd5423e36854f3565572.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "看例子：",
      "file": "zh-cn-2b52237702b27303d3a38852a8d008c52dbb825a.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "I am special.",
      "file": "en-us-30659168470ea344e663e832d4071108350f3afd.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "You are special.",
      "file": "en-us-bd168e4be2ccb03a768f5e99a6affc68421f8f80.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "He is special.",
      "file": "en-us-16532c2721b9ac71a837d574e6544ce38cdaa297.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "She is special.",
      "file": "en-us-5c8404f35b519d351ea9495b1ec21edc456b1f43.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "每个人都很特别",
      "file": "zh-cn-dbd32e676cd54d373cfc3f25ef9bfc4508fb3672.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "上帝认识每一个人",
      "file": "zh-cn-af6d1d44c50c2123c6b46805e0df482a5f4d6fc5.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "总结",
      "file": "zh-cn-ac47ec5504b1af7466662f04b2343ee4c68813ed.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "这节课我们学会说自己和别人",
      "file": "zh-cn-4c1a6495682cb81d89bcab616c22cf12f936b221.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "学会和别人说话，也学会说别人",
      "file": "zh-cn-cfc66196cd23ad8a7c71758180cdfd19688474d7.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "现在你可以说简单的句子了",
      "file": "zh-cn-8d0723043e76d8e00a7964b0f4439dc4457743a6.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "记住：上帝认识你的名字，你很特别",
      "file": "zh-cn-2927d44035bd471a74b6fb798b0ee8445728672e.mp3"
    }
  ]
}